<% content_for(:title) { "Privacy Policy - Prompt" } %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="mt-8 prose prose-indigo">
    <p class="text-gray-600">Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">We collect information you provide when creating an account, submitting maintenance requests, and using our services. This includes your name, email address, and property-related information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">We use your information to provide and improve our property management services, communicate with you about maintenance requests, and ensure the security of your account.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. Your passwords are encrypted and we use secure connections for data transmission.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at support@propman.com.</p>
  </div>
</div>
